    p "물론, 다른 데로 가자."

# game/LivingRoom.rpy:329
translate korean TalkNoah_8c549813:

    # r "Then I better head out."
    r "그러면, 저는 먼저 가보는 게 좋을 것 같아요."

# game/LivingRoom.rpy:330
translate korean TalkNoah_53bc1d59:

    # r "I'll be better on my own."
    r "혼자 있는게 편해서요."

# game/LivingRoom.rpy:331
translate korean TalkNoah_1d83294d:

